snippet.title: World Stadium 4 (PS1) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of World Stadium 4, a 2000 baseball video game for the PlayStation 1 by Namco. Namco All-Stars vs. Yakult Swallows at the Mappy Stadium.
